Package it.polimi.ingsw.messages

Class MessageFromServer

java.lang.Object
it.polimi.ingsw.messages.MessageFromServer
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class MessageFromServer extends Object implements Serializable
MessageFromServer is the object that a client send to the server in the socket output stream. The message contains a header (of type ServerMessageHeader) and a payload (of type MessagePayload).
